  "detailed_description": "\"DogDogDog\" is a horror adventure game set in modern times.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ Story<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRecently, you have been feeling like someone is stalking you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEvery day, you feel anxious, sensing eyes and hearing noises all around you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSuddenly, you remember the pet dog you used to have.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd then, you encounter a \"DOG\"...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYet life goes on.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ Game Features<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- A walking simulator where various events occur as you walk.<br />\r\n- Progress the story by examining objects.<br />\r\n- There are no quest markers or time limits, allowing for relaxed gameplay.<br />\r\n- Experience occasional terror from the appearance of dogs.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlaytime: 10 to 30 minutes<br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ Streaming Guidelines<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Streaming is possible without permission for individuals and companies alike.",
  "about_the_game": "\"DogDogDog\" is a horror adventure game set in modern times.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ Story<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRecently, you have been feeling like someone is stalking you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEvery day, you feel anxious, sensing eyes and hearing noises all around you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSuddenly, you remember the pet dog you used to have.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd then, you encounter a \"DOG\"...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYet life goes on.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ Game Features<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- A walking simulator where various events occur as you walk.<br />\r\n- Progress the story by examining objects.<br />\r\n- There are no quest markers or time limits, allowing for relaxed gameplay.<br />\r\n- Experience occasional terror from the appearance of dogs.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlaytime: 10 to 30 minutes<br />\r\n<br />\r\n◆ Streaming Guidelines<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Streaming is possible without permission for individuals and companies alike.",
